  "text": "No. of other genes in minimal deleted region (chromosome 15), described previously (7). Tumors were collected when mice became moribund. The SB tumor panel we used in our analysis is described in detail in Collier and colleagues [CITATION_1] , with the exception of 10 tumors, which were on a Bloom heterozygous background. [CITATION_2] Immunophenotyping of SB tumors revealed that the majority are of T-cell origin [CITATION_3] . Immunophenotyping of the MuLV tumors (6) indicated that they are either of T-cell or B-cell origin.",
